    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=j8ra9sbv59]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=j8ra9sbv59]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608796697/CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758294555248&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=759\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608796697/CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758294555248&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1073\" data-width=\"1074\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608796706\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608796697\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"64a08c3b-7bea-46d8-a9a2-4ea38f76de81\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608796697/CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758294555248&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1074&amp;height=1073 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608796697/CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758294555248&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=759 1x\" /></span><h1 id=\"BestPractices-PxrSurface-UnderstandingthebasicdesignofPxrSurface.\">Understanding the basic design of PxrSurface.</h1><p>The primary material used for making objects, props, and characters in RenderMan is the <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-26.pixar.com/space/REN26/19661415\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrSurface</u></a> material. </p><p>This is a single (and therefore &quot;monolithic&quot;) material used for all kinds of shading jobs. Each section of the material represents a particular &quot;lobe&quot; of the material.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"CookiesNMilk_new_pxrsurface.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608796697/CookiesNMilk_new_pxrsurface.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758294806847&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=701\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608796697/CookiesNMilk_new_pxrsurface.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758294806847&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"928\" data-width=\"1005\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608632870\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"CookiesNMilk_new_pxrsurface.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608796697\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"0137fbd9-6c1f-4420-a5b7-2c0a45573b44\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608796697/CookiesNMilk_new_pxrsurface.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758294806847&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1005&amp;height=928 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608796697/CookiesNMilk_new_pxrsurface.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758294806847&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=701 1x\" /></span><p>A few examples of these lobes are:</p><ul><li><p>Diffuse</p></li><li><p>Specular</p></li><li><p>Rough Specular</p></li><li><p>Sub-Surface</p></li><li><p>etc.</p></li></ul><p>Each of these has its own set of controls for defining the&nbsp;look and how they combine with the other lobes through gain or weighting.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"a7ead3c4-8739-4199-bb38-f69a79707a55\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Why is it called a &quot;lobe&quot;? </p><p>You can visualize how a material reflects or transmits light based on its distribution function; these are usually visualized as a lobe (an elongated shape showing sharpness, power, and direction) in 2D or 3D. You can find out more on <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bidirectional_scattering_distribution_function\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>Wikipedia</u></a>.</p></div></div><p /><hr /><h3 id=\"BestPractices-PxrSurface-NextSteps\"><span data-colorid=\"j8ra9sbv59\">Next Steps</span></h3><p>So, now you have a basic understanding of the monolithic shader's design, the mighty PxrSurface, let&rsquo;s learn the basics of textures in the next lesson.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/608829441/Best+Practices+-+Modeling\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608829441\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"previousLesson.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608796697/previousLesson.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758295895019&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=46\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608796697/previousLesson.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758295895019&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"67\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"607846814\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"previousLesson.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608796697\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"b2a870b8-a675-4db4-a42c-83ab2d350d68\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608796697/previousLesson.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758295895019&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=67 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608796697/previousLesson.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758295895019&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=46 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/608862209/Best+Practices+-+Textures\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608862209\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"nextLesson.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608796697/nextLesson.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758295895058&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=46\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608796697/nextLesson.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758295895058&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"67\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"607846821\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"nextLesson.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608796697\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"bcf4a192-f8a9-492b-a247-4c8bc4d4fe1c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608796697/nextLesson.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758295895058&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=67 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608796697/nextLesson.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758295895058&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=46 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png\" width=\"100\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608796697/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758295895078&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608796697/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758295895078&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"100\" data-width=\"100\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"607846827\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608796697\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"0eda9d66-96ef-4741-a3a2-0c0ee61eec68\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608796697/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758295895078&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608796697/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758295895078&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100 1x\" /></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
